PortSystem                  1.0
categories                  x11
maintainers                 {gcenx @gcenx}
license                     GPL, LGPL2.1, MPL

supported_archs             noarch
platforms                   darwin
description                 Wine's built-in replacement for Microsoft's .NET Framework
name                        wine-mono
set my_name                 wine-mono

